OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from phone
OL,4,Ctheft as incidents spike over summer
OL,6,FWith the summer holidays in full-flow,
OL,7,Fphone thefts are on the rise and, with
OL,8,Fthem, new warnings about the
OL,9,Fheightened risk. To combat the
OL,10,Fseasonal spike - a potential new
OL,11,Fsolution is being trialled, as ITV
OL,12,FNews Consumer Editor Chris Choi reports
OL,14,FThere are new warnings about the
OL,15,Fheightened risks of phone theft during
OL,16,Fthe summer holidays, at home, and
OL,17,Foverseas.
OL,19,FAs we relax outdoors, at festivals or
OL,20,Fin pavement cafes, there's a growing
OL,21,Fthreat.
