OL,4,Ctheft as incidents spike over summer
OL,6,FBut coinciding with this summer spike
OL,7,Fin phone snatching, a potential new
OL,8,Fsolution is being trialled.
OL,10,FMobile phone thieves are getting more
OL,11,Fmobile - on mopeds and bikes, every
OL,12,Fday, there are hundreds of victims.
OL,14,FToday, new research shows almost 90%
OL,15,Fof us see phone theft as a big worry.
OL,17,FNow there's a new potential solution.
OL,18,FIt's a line of vibrant colour along
OL,19,Fthe pavement, with warnings to "mind
OL,20,Fthe grab".
