OL,6,FIt's designed to grab your attention
OL,7,Fbefore anyone grabs your phone.
OL,9,FThe bright purple line is placed along
OL,10,Fthe kerbside on one of the most
OL,11,Fnotorious streets of all for phone
OL,12,Ftheft ` London's Oxford Street, the
OL,13,Fheart of an area with a phone theft
OL,14,Fevery 15 minutes on average.
OL,16,FNew research from across the UK shows
OL,17,Fthe risks:
OL,19,FMeanwhile, on holidays overseas, it's
OL,20,Fthe same old sorry tale.
