OL,3,CHow to protect yourself from phone
OL,4,Ctheft as incidents spike over summer
OL,6,F"San Francisco has kill switches on
OL,7,Fall phones sold.
OL,9,F"Barcelona, they've increased plain-
OL,10,Fclothed and uniformed patrols in those
OL,11,Fhotspot areas.
OL,13,F"Places like Japan have street
OL,14,Fannouncements now to remind people
OL,15,Fwhen they're going out and about.
OL,17,F"It's great that we are starting to
OL,18,Fsee a shift around the world from
OL,19,Freactive to a proactive response."
